We next carried out the nonadiabatic (NA) molecular dynamics with decoherence-induced surface hopping (DISH) approach to analysis the charge carrier dynamics of hematite, and the simulated data are shown in Fig. 5g–i. Fitting the curves to an exponent, Pt=exp(−tτ)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
